{"tid":1580821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"珠江橋牌豆豉鯪魚驗出孔雀石綠　食安中心：正追查食品來源","createTime":"2019-09-19T09:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T16:25:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"981f74af3993fffd0d42dc6e2c07bd6165291b56","tid":1580821,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190919/s00001/d6a4befe0ce566b71f70aceb3c7a1c30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190919%2Fs00001%2Fd6a4befe0ce566b71f70aceb3c7a1c30.jpg&h=ff4734e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食物安全中心今日（19日）公布，北角一間超級市場出售的「珠江橋牌豆豉鯪魚」含微量孔雀石綠，已知會涉事商戶停售有關批次產品，如有足夠證據，將提出檢控，現正追查有關食品的來源。<br />\n<br />\n該批「珠江橋牌豆豉鯪魚」罐頭原產地為中國，每罐淨重150克，到期日（此日期前最佳）為2022年2月24日。食安中心透過恆常的食物監測計劃，從北角一超級市場抽取有關罐頭鯪魚樣本作檢測，結果顯示，樣本含10億分之0.74孔雀石綠。<br />\n<br />\n食安中心指出，孔雀石綠是一種工業染料，被使用作治理魚類疾病，目前很多國家已禁止在食用動物中使用孔雀石綠；香港法例亦規定，所有在本港出售的食物均不能含有孔雀石綠，違者最高可被罰款5萬元及監禁6個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190919/s00001/1568882056611/%e7%8f%a0%e6%b1%9f%e6%a9%8b%e7%89%8c%e8%b1%86%e8%b1%89%e9%af%aa%e9%ad%9a%e9%a9%97%e5%87%ba%e5%ad%94%e9%9b%80%e7%9f%b3%e7%b6%a0-%e9%a3%9f%e5%ae%89%e4%b8%ad%e5%bf%83-%e6%ad%a3%e8%bf%bd%e6%9f%a5%e9%a3%9f%e5%93%81%e4%be%86%e6%ba%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190919%2Fs00001%2F1568882056611%2F%25e7%258f%25a0%25e6%25b1%259f%25e6%25a9%258b%25e7%2589%258c%25e8%25b1%2586%25e8%25b1%2589%25e9%25af%25aa%25e9%25ad%259a%25e9%25a9%2597%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%25ad%2594%25e9%259b%2580%25e7%259f%25b3%25e7%25b6%25a0-%25e9%25a3%259f%25e5%25ae%2589%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25bf%2583-%25e6%25ad%25a3%25e8%25bf%25bd%25e6%259f%25a5%25e9%25a3%259f%25e5%2593%2581%25e4%25be%2586%25e6%25ba%2590&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5YleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=21c9fec7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190919%2Fs00001%2F1568882056611%2F%25e7%258f%25a0%25e6%25b1%259f%25e6%25a9%258b%25e7%2589%258c%25e8%25b1%2586%25e8%25b1%2589%25e9%25af%25aa%25e9%25ad%259a%25e9%25a9%2597%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%25ad%2594%25e9%259b%2580%25e7%259f%25b3%25e7%25b6%25a0-%25e9%25a3%259f%25e5%25ae%2589%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%25bf%2583-%25e6%25ad%25a3%25e8%25bf%25bd%25e6%259f%25a5%25e9%25a3%259f%25e5%2593%2581%25e4%25be%2586%25e6%25ba%2590&h=80b617e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190919/s00001/1568882056611/%e7%8f%a0%e6%b1%9f%e6%a9%8b%e7%89%8c%e8%b1%86%e8%b1%89%e9%af%aa%e9%ad%9a%e9%a9%97%e5%87%ba%e5%ad%94%e9%9b%80%e7%9f%b3%e7%b6%a0-%e9%a3%9f%e5%ae%89%e4%b8%ad%e5%bf%83-%e6%ad%a3%e8%bf%bd%e6%9f%a5%e9%a3%9f%e5%93%81%e4%be%86%e6%ba%90</a>"},{"pid":"f6ecde9492693d6c83eab0c86f050f085aa25a89","tid":1580821,"uid":4917,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:06:11.000Z","msg":"係人都知來源係中國"},{"pid":"659523f585cd79062c7056339021b1424c149da4","tid":1580821,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6ecde9492693d6c83eab0c86f050f085aa25a89","tid":1580821,"uid":4917,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:06:11.000Z","msg":"係人都知來源係中國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6858371fdaa71df5dc2d1846e3905888bd43cf2","tid":1580821,"uid":81273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"目前很多國家已禁止在食用動物中使用孔雀石綠"},{"pid":"e9e4535c8d840f781ab4d21574de33bb61ff37fc","tid":1580821,"uid":130950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"之前唔係都有俾人驗出過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e372cbcb9aac68b2474a60471917c5f6c49b4b","tid":1580821,"uid":74888,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9e4535c8d840f781ab4d